Package com.oracle.coherence.grpc.client

An implementation of a Coherence Java gRPC client.
Since:
20.06
Author:
Jonathan Knight 2019.11.01
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GrpcRemoteSession.SessionDeactivationListener
    A listener that will be called when a session is closed.
    NamedCacheService
    A gRPC NamedCache service.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AsyncNamedCacheClient<K,​V>
    Implementation of a NamedCache.
    AsyncNamedCacheClient.Builder<K,​V>
    A Builder of AsyncNamedCacheClient instances.
    AsyncNamedCacheClient.FutureStreamObserver<T,​R>
    A StreamObserver that completes a CompletableFuture.
    AsyncNamedCacheClient.WrapperDeactivationListener<K,​V>
    A DeactivationListener that wraps client NamedCacheDeactivationListener.
    ClientGrpcMpExtension
    A GrpcMpExtension that will only be executed in an environment where there is also a Helidon gRPC MP server.
    CoherenceClientExtension
    A gRPC client side CDI Extension.
    DaemonPoolExecutor
    An Executor that uses a DaemonPool to execute tasks.
    DaemonPoolExecutor.Builder
    A builder of DaemonPoolExecutor instances.
    GrpcChannelBuilder
    A builder of gRPC ManagedChannels.
    GrpcChannelBuilder.Builder
    A builder to build a GrpcChannelBuilder.
    GrpcRemoteSession
    A client Session that connects to a remote gRPC proxy.
    GrpcRemoteSession.Builder
    A builder of GrpcRemoteSession instances.
    NamedCacheProducer
    A CDI producer for NamedCache gRPC service clients.
    RemoteCollection<K,​V,​T>
    A base class for implementations of collections related to a remote AsyncNamedCacheClient, for example key set, entry set and values.
    RemoteCollection.EntryAdvancer<K,​V>
    A PagedIterator.Advancer to support a PagedIterator over an entry set.
    RemoteCollection.EntryResultMapEntry
    A Map.Entry implementation that wraps a EntryResult.
    RemoteEntrySet<K,​V>
    A base class for NamedCache entry set implementations.
    RemoteKeySet<K,​V>
    A base class for NamedCache key set implementations.
    RemoteKeySet.KeysAdvancer
    An PagedIterator.Advancer to support a PagedIterator over this key set.
    RemoteSessions
    A CDI producer for GrpcRemoteSession instances.
    RemoteSessions.NameOption
    A Session.Option to use to specify the name for a session.
    RemoteSessions.ScopeOption
    A Session.Option to use to specify the scope name for a session.
    RemoteValues<K,​V>
    A base class for NamedCache values collection implementations.
    RemoteValues.ValuesIterator<K,​V>
    An Iterator to iterate over the cache values.
